                <head>No. 826<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On November 2, <persName>H.C. Hansen</persName>, Foreign Minister of Denmark,
                    attended a luncheon hosted by Secretary <persName corresp="#p_DULLESJF1"
                        >Dulles</persName> at Blair House. No record of a conversation has been
                    found in Department of State files.</p>
                <p>
                    <persName corresp="#p_LANGEH1">Halvard Lange</persName>, Foreign Minister of
                    Norway, visited Secretary <persName corresp="#p_DULLESJF1">Dulles</persName> on
                    November 15 to discuss the forthcoming Bermuda Conference and <gloss
                        target="#t_NAC1">NAC</gloss> meetings and certain aspects of the proceedings
                    at the United Nations, which <persName corresp="#p_LANGEH1">Lange</persName> was
                    then attending. A brief <pb facs="0684" n="1774" xml:id="pg_1774"/> record of
                    this conversation, dated November 16, is in file 757.13/111653.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
